Before starting any MARQ Cortex architecture, migration, or data-platform task, read:

1. `MARQ_CORTEX_CONSTITUTION.md` — locked operating principles (v1.1)
2. `prompts/MARQ-CLAUDE-AGENT-SYSTEM-PROMPT-v1.0.md` — agent operating contract
3. `ARCHITECT.md` — repository map and task lookup

Migration sprints must obey **Article 17 — Runtime Authority Protection**: validation precedes authority; KV remains authoritative until per-domain cutover gates pass.

Do not store secrets in repository files or generated reports.
